  {\Large {\bf \hspace*{-0.2cm} SUSY Glue-Balls,\protect\vspace*{0.2cm} \\ 
      Dynamical Symmetry Breaking\protect\vspace*{0.3cm}\\
      and Non-Holomorphic Potentials.}}
      \vspace*{1cm} \\

